title: 2019 Week 12 Recap
itunes:title: 2019 Week 12 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap all of the games from week 12 including the Patriots beating the Cowboys in the rain (03:09), the Buffalo Bills stomping out the Broncos (28:25), and the Jets (35:23) and Browns (57:46) winning again. As always, they recap the Sunday Night Football game, this week between the Packers and 49ers.(1:17:01)
